Initialize prisma:
npx prisma init

Create initial migration:
npx prisma migrate dev --name init

Generate new database schema:
npx prisma generate

Reset database:
npx prisma migrate reset

Open prisma studio:
npx prisma studio

Push changes from schema.prisma to DB:
npx prisma db push

